name: NATURE UNVEILED #6 (The Lion King)
description:
"Once a wise man told you that your kingdom was not of this world.
You have not understood it until today.
You are still here.
Here where you do not belong.
Why you do not want to understand,
that we are the Kings here?
Kings without a Kingdom.
Now get the hell out of here before it's too late for you.
Let us finally alone
LET US BE KINGS !! "

200 DPI, 4000 x 8000, JPEG

(Caesar's Words from the "Manifesto of the Animals/der Lotuszwinger")
